title: Severn - A Beginning EP (2008) [FLAC][cxcr6-003]
description:
Brought to you by CXCR6 records: 
[url]http://www.cxcr6.com[/url]

Severn has been creating musics of various forms for about twelve years. His sound has taken in many different influences and becomes a hybrid of intense industrial rhythmic programming with meldoramatic songwriting that takes you on a journey exploring each layer and each corner of the musical idea and developing into a mad cacophany of bouncing opera-core. You will either love it or hate it.

This album is absolutely fucking amazing.
